				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/Chu-b%E1%BA%A1c-Kim-S%C6%A1n-t%C3%A2n-th%E1%BB%A9/poem-WUEKpcJMdn8BqwsG0n1DOA">Chu bạc Kim Sơn tân thứ - 舟泊金山津次</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%90%C4%83ng-Qu%E1%BA%BF/author-lKB5JGuV47V39O71nzayyw">Trương Đăng Quế</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-K%E1%BB%B3/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Th%C3%A1nh-qu%C3%A1n-t%E1%BB%B1/poem-UaeAJarCM1MsQDdHCNPCBg">Đại Thánh quán tự - 大聖觀寺</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-K%E1%BB%B3/author-6RHyKOpqR_VZ_nmIcRKQxw">Trần Kỳ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/%C4%90%C3%ACnh-th%C3%AD-%C4%91%E1%BB%91i-s%C3%A1ch/poem-rF91EB30-zT6DtZAE4A1yw">Đình thí đối sách - 廷試對策</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-Ph%C3%B9ng/author-GfNq85EUzTvOO-A-Y5zO9w">Phan Đình Phùng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-%E1%BA%A8n/Ho%C3%A0i-T%E1%BB%8Bnh-%C4%90%E1%BB%99-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem--HVBj6lmUxMfcO3RNykZRQ">Hoài Tịnh Độ thi kỳ 3 - 懷凈土詩其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Li%C3%AAn-%E1%BA%A8n/author-PJ6V09BOBhth9bLNhZ-Xyw">Liên Ẩn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/M%C3%A3n-giang-h%E1%BB%93ng-Giang-h%C3%A0nh-ho%E1%BA%A1-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-T%E1%BA%BF-%C3%94ng-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-jHRmteBFvMYWAHouxxR9Pw">Mãn giang hồng - Giang hành hoạ Dương Tế Ông vận - 滿江紅－江行和楊濟翁韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A2n-Kh%C3%AD-T%E1%BA%ADt/author-cR0yq4BrF6xGIKZCvJGLSA">Tân Khí Tật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/Minh-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-gia-hu%E1%BA%A5n/poem-3aa2tlihTrwlAHWnLopSow">Minh Đạo gia huấn - 明道家訓</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C3%ACnh-H%E1%BA%A1o/author-f6hExEIODG8dBbnhIj50jQ">Trình Hạo</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/Ph%E1%BB%A5c-qu%C3%A1i/poem-FK6HDah2AjWt_doNmOZJqQ">Phục quái - 復卦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-B%E1%BB%89nh-Khi%C3%AAm/author-Rv6locqJPIunovJpeqDNxA">Nguyễn Bỉnh Khiêm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BB%B1-Kh%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%A9-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-qjyFFM43hYrWKw3L9DkOXA">Tặng Vương nhị thập tứ thị ngự Khế tứ thập vận - 贈王二十四侍禦契四十韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Du%E1%BA%ADt/T%E1%BB%B1-v%E1%BB%8Bnh/poem-HBTXuo3NvXzWMHqWNqcazQ">Tự vịnh - 自詠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ph%E1%BA%A1m-Th%E1%BA%ADn-Du%E1%BA%ADt/author-rOATA3YE3xI-b4gI-_iYag">Phạm Thận Duật</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/Xu%C3%A2n-nh%E1%BA%ADt-tuy%E1%BB%87t-c%C3%BA-th%E1%BA%ADp-th%E1%BB%A7-k%E1%BB%B3-03/poem-XTnru3ZF6p5W6ZzzR0uMaw">Xuân nhật tuyệt cú thập thủ kỳ 03 - 春日絕句十首其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
